tool_description: API used to retrieve data from Google search results in real time. Support web search and image search
name: Google Search_v3
title: Google Search

api_list.name: Image Search
api_list.description: This endpoint is used for image searches

parameters.name: start
parameters.description: The index of the first result to return.

parameters.name: num
parameters.description:
Number of search results to return.
Valid values are integers between 1 and 20, inclusive

parameters.name: gl
parameters.description: The gl parameter value is a two-letter country code. The gl parameter boosts search results whose country of origin matches the parameter value.

parameters.name: lr
parameters.description: Restricts the search to documents written in a particular language

api_list.name: Web Search
api_list.description: This endpoint is used for web searches
